Package entities

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
entities.Movie
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Movie>
public class Movie extends Object implements Comparable<Movie>, Serializable
Movie is a class that stores information about a movie, including its name, length, status, synopsis, director, cast, total rating, review count, and ticket sales
